description: This file is a C header file defining internal API prototypes for the HttpAtoCgiEnv object, including functions for creating code and name tables, and for retrieving atom codes and names.

methods.name: HttpAtoCgiEnvCreateCodeTable
methods.description: Initializes or creates the internal code table used by HttpAtoCgiEnv.

methods.name: HttpAtoCgiEnvCreateNameTable
methods.description: Initializes or creates the internal name table used by HttpAtoCgiEnv.

methods.name: HttpAtoCgiEnvGetAtomCode
methods.description: Retrieves the code corresponding to the given atom name.

methods.name: HttpAtoCgiEnvGetAtomName
methods.description: Retrieves the atom name corresponding to the given code.
